{
  "stem": "717.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There were a couple guys that were there that didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They said, after the war, he's a Jewish guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We suffered enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Nah, we don't want to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So finally, he told me-- he called me in that office and said, look Jack.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You don't have any witnesses today.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He's gone.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I've got to let him go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he let him go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But we'll come back to him later in Australia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I met him in Australia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When these guys took me out-- when they hid me in a different barrack-- we still stayed in Birkenau for a while.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I think in Birkenau I stayed altogether maybe two weeks, three weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And then they picked out a group and they tattooed me, which meant-- and they gave me a uniform, that black and white.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "You know, the striped uniform with the hat and all that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I was very proud.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I'm-- I'm one of the elite.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I'm wearing a uniform, and I already have a number on my hand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And in a short while, they put us on trucks and sent us to the camp, another concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "That here is my number-- B10237.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "You know it's funny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I was born the 13th, and everything I do comes up with a 13.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And my numbers, totaled up, also make 13.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They sent us, not very far from a-- from a camp that belonged-- was under the jurisdiction of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "The camp was called Trzebinia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "There was a bombed oil refinery there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "They had oil refineries there before the war, and it was bombed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And what we did there, we build it up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "The huge oil refineries, you built with bricks, up, like a wall around it.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
